WEBVTT

00:04:57.240 --> 00:05:00.623
Think of your poo and pee
as a health smoothie for a tree.

00:05:00.647 --> 00:05:04.470
(Laughter)

00:05:05.357 --> 00:05:07.166
The other bummer going on here

00:05:07.190 --> 00:05:11.205
is that we're quickly moving
all the drugs we take into our waterways.

00:05:11.971 --> 00:05:16.202
The average wastewater treatment plant
can remove maybe half of the drugs

00:05:16.226 --> 00:05:17.439
that come in.

00:05:17.910 --> 00:05:20.540
The other half goes
right out the other side.

00:05:20.564 --> 00:05:24.020
Consider what a cocktail
of pharmaceuticals --

00:05:24.044 --> 00:05:26.065
hormones, steroids, Vicodin --

00:05:26.089 --> 00:05:27.872
does to a fish,

00:05:27.896 --> 00:05:29.118
to a dog,

00:05:29.142 --> 00:05:30.342
to a child.